aces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n//「港區國安法」未有具體條文，特首林鄭月娥昨於行會會議前見記者，被問及港區國安法會否凌駕《基本法》、人權法對港人保障時，她稱《公民權利和政治權利國際公約》（ICCPR）中，個人自由會受制於國家安全，「所以本身在國際層面，國家安全這件事會大至真的有一些根本性和凌駕性存在」，但法律如何平衡、司法機關如何可認為無違反個人權利，均要看過條文及應用時才知悉。//"},{"pid":"8c9a83a3296e6b0913b732d04487f3e471ea1f8a","tid":2069522,"uid":225818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T14:31:18.000Z","msg":"獨特優勢在「一國兩制」下受到充分保障。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲好意思出聲"},{"pid":"9aa31125099bc0def3425e3471b9f91701175321","tid":2069522,"uid":356500,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T14:33:53.000Z","msg":"又拎基本法出黎畀美國佬睇？"},{"pid":"866c7c16491144a40e58701e58ec71c64a5bf863","tid":2069522,"uid":146621,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"06e9af3c5c0bbfc618f93b2450c7aae041358629","tid":2069522,"uid":281328,"like":30,"dislike":1,"score":29,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T12:44:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>是日笑話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;有健全法律保障私隱，獨特優勢在「一國兩制」下受到充分保障&rdquo;"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T14:34:14.000Z","msg":"點解人地要貪你一國兩制<br />\n本身一國唔令人信服先要搞兩制出黎<br />\n而家一國大於兩制<br />\n人地唔驚死不如直接投資中國<br />\n一係就搵過第二個地方投資好過<br />\n講到一國兩制係皇恩浩盪咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9555056ba9c56c2f82df779e85b6f3a48c346149","tid":2069522,"uid":19501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T14:37:21.000Z","msg":"美國公然違反國際法，大波驊唔告美國政府就係港獨<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc7abf7185c1556b07cfa218539de72fff069672","tid":2069522,"uid":3172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"61c33158887f7d7cd35ac8ccf6596b4636ca3bde","tid":2069522,"uid":346701,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T13:25:12.000Z","msg":